General.Name: Federal International Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Federal International Holdings Berhad manufactures and trades in furniture products primarily in Malaysia. The company operates through Manufacturing and Trading of Furniture, Renovation and Interior Design, Construction Business, and Investment Holding segments. The company trades in home furnishings, home appliances, and general building materials, as well as acts as general contractor for construction works; engages in the renovation and interior design of offices and hotels, including supply of furniture and fittings; and operates as a designer, assembler, integrator, decorator, furnisher, woodworker, consultant, and contractor for various types of projects. In addition, it is involved in the manufacturing of modular caseworks, shop fixtures and fitting, and furniture comprising wall and base cabinets, shelving, display cases, countertop, kitchen furniture, and panels for corporate clients; and construction of real estate, including residential and commercial properties. The company was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
